supposed to make this

17:06.214 --> 17:08.848
look like a robbery, and now it does.

17:08.883 --> 17:11.150
Boom, problem solved.

17:11.185 --> 17:15.954
So your CSI instincts prompted
you to be that damn stupid, huh?

17:15.990 --> 17:18.023
Don't you realize that the more you lie,

17:18.059 --> 17:20.159
