24:35.672 --> 24:38.172
- Hey, Pol.
- How you doing?

24:40.076 --> 24:41.175
Oh.

24:41.210 --> 24:43.674
You don't look so good, pretty baby.

24:44.547 --> 24:46.080
Rough night?

24:49.285 --> 24:50.685
- Hey, Dean.
- Hey, Deanie.

24:50.720 --> 24:52.787
I thought you were
working out with Monty.

24:52.822 --> 24:53.954
