or you're against me.

25:15.345 --> 25:17.041
Pick your fancy.

25:17.613 --> 25:19.347
Dean.

25:19.382 --> 25:20.614
Dean.

25:22.251 --> 25:23.617
Let's talk about this.

25:23.653 --> 25:24.819
No.

25:24.854 --> 25:26.354
Dean, ‭what are you gonna do,

25:26.389 --> 25:28.089
