41:58.748 --> 42:01.018
- [Laughs]
- Nail Artisans.

42:01.053 --> 42:03.221
UNCLE DADDY: This is Clay.

42:03.256 --> 42:05.186
Hey. Hey, Clay. Is everything all right?

42:05.221 --> 42:07.221
Yeah, things are just fine, Miss Desna.

42:07.257 --> 42:09.791
- Is this a good time?
- Yeah, what's going on?

42:09.826 --> 42:13.461
Well, Roller's killers
have beautifully transitioned,

42:13.496 --> 42:15.496
thanks to some mercurial angels

42:15.532 --> 42:18.099
led by my handsome nephew, Bryce.

42:19.715 --> 42:22.565
Are you saying that
Roller's killers are dead?

42:23.886 --> 42:25.586
Who... Who did this to him?

42:25.775 --> 42:27.241
Dirty mothers.

42:27.277 --> 42:30.077
Ran some high-end real-estate
office across the state,

42:30.113 --> 42:32.046
dealing drugs ‭out of every one of them.

42:32.081 --> 42:33.948
Someone's conscience
got the best of them

42:33.983 --> 42:35.787
and they tipped off the police.

42:36.205 --> 42:38.372
Luckily, I got some Cops on the tit,

42:38.397 --> 42:41.632
and they, uh, gave me a head start.

42:41.991 --> 42:43.658
[Quietly] My God.

42:43.693 --> 42:45.526
Listen, uh, I just...

42:45.562 --> 42:47.128
I just wanted to say sorry

42:47.163 --> 42:50.231
if this investigation
caused you any pain or hardship.

42:50.968 --> 42:54.235
And give my regards
to Virginia, as well.

42:54.270 --> 42:58.906
My nephew used to say,
"It's a new era, y'all."

42:59.691 --> 43:01.646
- [Beeps]
- Shit.

43:02.125 --> 43:03.624
Who found them?

43:05.955 --> 43:07.788
Was it Bryce? Did he do it?

43:09.226 --> 43:12.427
[Sobs]

43:12.822 --> 43:14.522
Don't cry, baby, don't cry.

43:14.557 --> 43:15.656
[Sobbing]

43:15.692 --> 43:17.592
Don't cry. Don't cry. Don't cry.

43:17.627 --> 43:20.661
[Crying] No!

43:20.697 --> 43:25.800
No! [Sobbing]

43:27.337 --> 43:28.589
Dean.

43:37.146 --> 43:43.618
Deanie, I... I am so sorry
for what they did to you.

43:43.653 --> 43:46.274
I wish I had known back then.

43:48.892 --> 43:51.779
They're not gonna be able
to hurt you anymore.

43:52.662 --> 43:54.395
Ho-How do you know?

43:54.430 --> 43:56.416
I know. I ju...

43:57.634 --> 43:59.203
I just know.

44:01.217 --> 44:03.784
It's time to put all the...

44:04.173 --> 44:10.011
the pain behind us... the
Coombses, Roller, all of it.

44:12.155 --> 44:14.468
I need you to know
‭that we're safe now, baby.

44:16.586 --> 44:19.020
- Yeah.
- Yeah.

44:22.926 --> 44:26.093
[Opera Music Playing]

44:29.732 --> 44:36.737
[Operatic Singing In Italian]

44:54.924 --> 44:57.458
[Hoarsely] Help me.

44:57.493 --> 44:59.360
Help me.

44:59.395 --> 45:01.362
Help me. Help... Help me.

45:01.397 --> 45:02.665
Mr. Emerson.

45:02.700 --> 45:03.964
No, I'm Roller.

45:04.000 --> 45:05.585
You're alive.

45:05.620 --> 45:07.988
I need water.

45:08.024 --> 45:09.607
Who are you?

45:10.633 --> 45:16.489
I'm your bleeding heart of love,
Mr. Emerson.

45:16.899 --> 45:20.501
Oh, welcome to Tuscany.

45:20.950 --> 45:23.818
[Singing Continues]

45:27.624 --> 45:30.558
[Vocalizing]

45:30.593 --> 45:34.044
- You're finally home.
- I need help.

